<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB07826</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT TO ESTABLISH THE PHILIPPINE ENVIRONMENTAL ASSESSMENT SYSTEM, AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Adopts an Environmental Assessment System which is composed of: a.) Strategic Environmental Assessment (SEA) for policies, plans and programs to ensure that Philippines’ development will be sustainable; and b.) Environment Impact Assessment (EIA) for specific projects which have potential significant adverse impact on the environment.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ALIAS NAME : “Philippine Environmental Assessment System Act of 2018.” </td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>BERTIZ, ANICETO &quot;JOHN&quot; III D.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2018-05-31</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Silverio (000 2018-08-06)</td><td>2. Sy-Alvarado (000 2018-08-07)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON NATURAL RESOURCES ON 2018-07-30</td></tr></table>